{
  "stem": "17001.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we got there, frozen off, so we went to the train station and we went there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had my father brother, my uncle, living not far from the train station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had a daughter the same age as I am, so we stayed there until it was time to go to school, because we would have to get out-- get out of the house 6 o'clock to take the train and the school started 8 o'clock, so we had time to spend there.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we would walk with my cousin to school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was all very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then in the-- '38, there started to get a lot of commotion there, with like the black-dressed soldiers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know where they came from.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they had-- going around and asking every Jewish family that they should donate money, because they want to erect a flagpole at middle of the marketplace.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And if you didn't give enough money, then they weren't satisfied.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there were times when they would take Jewish men up into the-- to the city hall and they would question and they would beat them and so on, because he didn't give enough money towards the flagpole.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were [INTERPOSING VOICES] Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were the hoodlums that-- that they-- they wore the black uniform.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- that was the beginning of the-- of the anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the beginning of the-- of the-- I-- I can't even remember the name of it, how you-- in Germany, they called it the-- the youth group.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Here, I don't know what [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They weren't young people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were hoodlums who didn't have a job.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were just out to get the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
